*** Context ***
+ Clear Workspace
+ A project is created in the workspace without Execution Environment
+ No Execution Environment is linked to the LDT

*** Actions ***
- Right-click on the project -> Properties
- Select Lua -> Build Path
- Select tab Libraries
- Click on Add Library...
- Select Lua Execution Environment -> Next
- Click on Configure -> Add...
- Select an Execution Environment to add -> Open -> Ok
- Click on Finish

*** Assertions ***
# The Execution Environment is linked to the LDT
# The Execution Environment is in the project
